Replace this file with the actual wireframe mockup for the AI Chat interface.
The AI Chat interface should show:
- Sidebar with conversation history list (previous chat sessions with timestamps)
- Main chat area with:
  - Header: "MedChain AI Assistant" with avatar icon
  - Message bubbles: user messages right-aligned (blue), AI responses left-aligned (gray)
  - AI responses formatted with markdown: headings, bullet points, bold text
  - Medical disclaimer banner at top of chat area
  - Typing indicator (animated dots) while AI is generating response
  - Input area at bottom with text input field and send button
  - Character counter showing remaining characters (max 2000)
  - Quick action buttons: "Analyze Symptoms", "Find Specialist", "Summarize Record"
